events.description: General Admission Pit - standing only no chairs Clear Bag Policy - The Petersen Events Center has a clear bag policy for ALL events. Small clutch purses (roughly the size of a hand) are allowed. Here are some details regarding the policy: Bags that are clear plastic, vinyl or PVC and do not exceed 12 inches x 6 inches x 12 inches One-gallon clear plastic freezer bag (Ziploc bag or similar) Logo on bag cannot exceed 4.5 inches tall by 3.4 inches wide Small clutch purses, approximately the size of a hand, or 4.5 inches x 6.5 inches with or without a handle or strap, are allowed. An exception will be made for medically necessary items after proper inspection at entry. Diaper Bags are permitted, but will be searched and tagged. For Premium Seating and Suites information please email peterseneventscenter@pitt.edu or call 412-648-3054
